Guacamole Recipe:
2 ripe avocados
1/2 red onion
1/4 garlic clove
coriander leaves
1/2 lemon juice
salt
olive oil

Instructions: 
chop the onion into very small cubes
mash the avocados and mix them with the onions and garlic
Add the lemon juice, the chopped coriander, salt and olive oil
Mix and enjoy!
